        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to <span class="matchaRose">Matcha</span> - Where Every Love Story is Celebrated!</h1>
            <div class="lead">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="matchaRose">Why Matcha?</h2>
                    <ul style="list-style-type: none;">
                        <li>üåà <strong>Inclusivity at the Core:</strong> Matcha celebrates diversity. No matter who you are, we welcome you with warmth and respect.</li>
                        <li>üíñ <strong class="matchaRose">Authentic Connections:</strong> Connect with genuine individuals who share your values and vision of love.</li>
                        <li>üåê <strong>Open to All Stories:</strong> Whether you're seeking traditional love or a unique connection, Matcha is where all love stories can thrive.</li>
