                    <li><strong class="matchaRose">Customize Your Preferences:</strong> Define your search criteria for matches that resonate with you.</li>
                    <li><strong>Communicate with Confidence:</strong> Exchange messages in a secure and friendly space.</li>
                    <li><strong class="matchaRose">Meet In Person:</strong> When you feel ready, transition from virtual to real-life connections.</li>
                </ol>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>
                <h5>Join Matcha today and explore a world of inclusivity where every love story is celebrated.</h5>
                <hr>
            </section>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="{{ path('security.registration') }}" role="button">Sign Up</a>
                    or
                    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="{{ path('security.login') }}" role="button">Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <a href="{{ path('security.new.password') }}"><p>Forget password ?</p></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
